<br>
We're allowed to use RA's, so will both have purge and IP.<br>
<br>
What do you guys think I should do?<br>
<br>
My plan<br>
- DA song (is resist song worth it)<br>
- DD,DD, sare then stay away and hope he blows purge to remove the snare<br>
- mezz, DD, DD fight<br>
