- DD, DD fight<br>
- mezz, rest<br>
- repeat last 3, using IP if needed.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c2a2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/bteamskald.showUserPublicProfile?gid=emblurr@teamskald>Emblurr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Participant</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#ff0000>(1/14/03 11:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=451.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> re:</span><hr size=1> How are your skills specced?<br>
